<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau hung inla, Edena thil lui,
 Hung mang intin Na gam nuom thil ingka;
 Hun mung ka ting,Na lopina haw chu,
 Pakna gi huihchim guolin leng ina.

[V2]
 Immanuel, Na hehpih kulh sungah,
 Buoina gal a lien ie hung nai kitin;
 Hung kit inla, Nang ka Bitna Na hi,
 Na hehpih kulhsungah aw,
 Buoina gal a lien ie.

[V3]
 2. Kipahna leh vangsakna ni lopi,
 Na lampi gal muongah ei pui zelin;
 Jordan luipi lien chu kinawk vielin,
 Kanaan gam hawih luigal chu kai tangka.

[V4]
 3. Vakhu guolin tha zakin leng thei leng,
 Ka damna kalvari tang tung ingting;
 Chun, zie mun chu ka pawtsan kittieng leh,
 Lalna gam nitum ngeilo zuon ingka.

[V5]
 4. Aw, ka damlai ni hi abeih tieng leh,
 Lawpna khawpi laituol a leng tangka;
 Kalvari thihna paka lasate,
 Kipahna tuoi theilo in zawm tang ka.</lyrics>
<title>Na Hehpih Kulh Sungah</title>
<author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>103</hymn_number>
</song>